underlying_goal: To transform a simple research notes file into a structured literature review on AI sandbagging, organized by deployment stage.
primary_success: Transformed a basic notes file into a comprehensive, well-structured literature review, organizing it by sandbagging stage and enriching it with several new, relevant papers and detailed summaries.
brief_summary: The user requested a restructure and expansion of a research document. The agent created a new literature review, organized it by the requested sandbagging stages (training, evals, deployment), and significantly enriched it by adding and summarizing several new, relevant research papers.
